"The Toast Alchemist: A Personalized Toast Sculpting Device" - A handheld device that analyzes the browning pattern of your toast in real-time and *actively reshapes* it with micro-precision laser technology. It learns your preferred toast profile, anticipates browning, and subtly corrects it. Includes a ‘Dramatic Black’ setting for a truly impressive presentation. Also, a companion app for documenting your toast-shaping journeys and sharing with the world. Bonus: integrated aromatherapy – a whiff of cinnamon or vanilla during the shaping process!